Ongoing development - currently not usable at all


Goals
- Having an tool which automatically deletes twitter tweets of a certain age
  (who is interested in old stuff anyway? Its just polluting the infophere)
- In the course of deleting tweets also remove associated tweetfile images

Configuration
*************

- Copy the file tweetdecayopts-template.py to tweetdecayopts.py
- Adapt the settings in tweetdecayopts.py
- Hide from other users with the command
  chmod og-rw tweetdecayopts.py

